Text: This ep was superb, I cant believe they are not going to renew this
SyFy never was very smart about renewing good shows.

That's because SyFy has to make lots of room for fake wrestling and Mega-Two-Headed Shark vs. Piranha-Bear-Octopus starring former 80's pop stars or Carmen Electra. There is no room for hit series like Stargate.
